Comment: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:30.68,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:90683,90683}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:36.06,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:92059,96063}{\i1}A poor girl raised\Nin the slums, Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:42.23,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:96063,102236}{\i1}Despite living in poverty, she always\Nbrightens her surroundings with smile and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:46.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:102236,106907}{\i1}With an innate fondness for music,\Nshe strives to become a professional singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:51.12,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:106907,111120}{\i1}While going through various struggles\Nand learning of the adult world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:56.50,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:111120,116500}{\i1}she boldly ventures into it with the dream\Nof becoming a star some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:05.92,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:120295,125926}{\i1}Thanks to help from her friends, she has received\Nan apprenticeship with a famous composer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.47,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:125926,128470}{\i1}Bearing with her teacher's\Nunpredictable mood swings,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:13.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:128470,133892}{\i1}she took the first step on a long\Nand steep road to starting her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:17.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:133892,137688}{\i1}In the meantime, a warm feeling\Nfor Fanni began to grow in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:26.19,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:139022,146196}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,4000,1.3,\1c&HD3F0CB&\3c&H020400&\4c&H000000&)}National New Year's\NRookie of the Year Championships{NOTE:日本新人王座決定戦}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:33.62,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:148157,153620}{\fad(0,500)\t(6299,7799,3,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)}— Episode 08 —\NThe Promise Between The Two{NOTE:第8話\\N二人の誓い}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.54,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:154371,156540}Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.33,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:157166,159334}We've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:42.58,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:159334,162588}Ladies and gentlemen, the fourth round.\NOnly one minute left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.84,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:162588,164840}Both contestants\Nare dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.55,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:164840,167551}Who will become\Nthe Rookie of the Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:54.30,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:170095,174308}Ah! Ishida throws a series of right straights\Nfollowed by a heavy uppercut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.93,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:174308,175934}{\i1}He doesn't hold back at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.89,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:175934,177895}{\i1}Ishida dominates the ring!{NOTE:決まったの夕べ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.73,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:177895,179730}{\i1}Ah! Referee steps in\Nto separate the boxers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.44,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:179730,181440}{\i1}It seems he's going\Nto end the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.02,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:183650,186028}{\i1}I will win.\NNo room for defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.61,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:186028,187613}{\i1}Watch me, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:10.57,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:187613,190574}{\i1}I will win today's game.\NFor your sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:195370,196163}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:196747,198081}Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.96,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:203712,206965}Nozomi-chan, leave it. If you don't hurry,\Nyou won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:30.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:206965,210260}Yeah, I know.\NThat's the last one, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:210260,212221}Are you sure\Nyou've finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:212221,214848}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.93,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:214848,216934}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:216934,218393}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:43.35,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:218977,223357}Don't worry about it, I'll finish it for you.\NHurry up and go see him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:223357,224650}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:48.40,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:224650,228403}Why are you still standing there?\NGo or I'll push you with this stick myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:230656,233158}I am in your debt, Sune-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:242292,243877}I hope you win, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:243877,246046}I won't accept a defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:21.60,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:257307,261603}And now for the main event: the battle\Nthat will decide the new Rookie of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:26.48,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:261603,266483}After 5 days of competitions, we will now\Nwitness the most awaited meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:30.23,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:266483,270237}The two contenders are\NFanni Moriyama and Condor Nakagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.32,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:270237,273323}It's the final match of East Japan\Nin bantamweight class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:36.11,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:273323,276118}This meeting will decide\Nwho of the two will be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:40.33,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:276118,280330}to fight the West Japan champion,\NLefty Hatamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.87,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:280330,282875}Fanni Moriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.58,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:282875,284585}Or Condor Nakagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:310527,311945}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.92,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:326835,329922}Moriyama's got Condor\NNakagawa in the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.88,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:329922,332883}Fanni's straights\Nare relentless tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.76,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:332883,334760}The match is\Ncompletely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.17,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:334760,337179}It's a fight on a level you wouldn't\Nexpect from new fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:42.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:340223,342017}{\i1}Good luck, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.15,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:357032,358158}Go to neutral corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.20,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:358158,359201}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.20,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:359201,360202}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.32,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:360202,361328}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.49,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:361328,362496}Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.66,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:362496,363664}Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.87,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:363664,364873}Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.99,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:364873,365999}Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.12,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:365999,367125}Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.12,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:367125,368126}Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.87,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{TIME:368126,369878}Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:376134,377386}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:382933,384518}Fanni! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:384518,385686}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.47,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:385686,386478}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:386478,389690}I saw the entire game.\NYou were amazing—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:30.77,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:389690,390774}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.77,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:392484,394778}What are you doing?\NYou've still got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.61,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:394778,396613}Come on. Don't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:38.19,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:396613,398198}Yes sir. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:400033,402786}What's his problem?\NYou've just won the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.82,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:402786,403829}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:47.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:403829,407541}As you see, I don't have the time\Nto talk with you at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.75,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:407541,410752}Could you wait for me\Nat the park nearby?{NOTE:裏の公園で待っててくれないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:410752,411461}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.13,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:411461,414131}Alright. I'll be there\Nas soon as I'm done with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:07:00.88,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:415632,420887}Now we will continue with\Nthe semi-final matches.{NOTE:では引き続いて本日のセミファイナル 8回戦を行います}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:07.56,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:420887,427561}In the red corner, the Japanese bantamweight\Nthird-ranker, Ishiguro Chodoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.98,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:428562,431982}It is true that you failed\Nto make weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:15.48,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:431982,435485}You'll have to see\Nuntil after the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.77,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:435485,437779}That's enough, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.61,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:437779,441616}We just want to know\Nhow things are before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.11,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:441616,443118}But I told you plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.07,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:443118,445078}But that last knockout\Nwas pretty good, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.08,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:445078,447080}Stop asking me\Nabout Fanni Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.45,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:447080,449458}But it really was a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.08,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:449458,451084}But his opponent—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:35.46,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:451084,455464}Alright, gentlemen, that's it. We're before\Nthe match and got to prepare. Time to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.92,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:456298,457924}Fanni, pass me the gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:38.71,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:457924,458717}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:467392,469936}{\i1}Fanni is doing his best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:469936,472272}{\i1}But he works\Nmuch harder than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:56.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:472272,476785}{\i1}I'm sure he'll become\Na champion soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:476785,479204}{\i1}But I'm not going to fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:13.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:483625,493844}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Music is my friend  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:22.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:493844,502561}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When things get hard,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  it stays with me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:32.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:502561,512404}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Heard alone it's lonely, but  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:41.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:512404,521037}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Heard together  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  it resonates with everyone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:50.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:521037,530213}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I hope the people  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  downtown can hear it  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:09:00.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:530213,540974}{\fad(0,1000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's believe in the tomorrow  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that will spread someday  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:546229,547314}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:562162,563288}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.66,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:564247,565665}That was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:28.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:566416,568919}Don't make me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:568919,572088}At any rate, it's rude\Nto make a lady wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:572088,574049}Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.26,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:574049,577260}But if I didn't come late, I'd probably\Nmiss the best scene of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:577260,579679}Never mind.\NCongratulations, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:579679,582432}Finally you can partake in\Nthe National Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:582432,585060}I believe in you.\NYou're unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.02,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:585060,588021}You can count on me, Nozomi.\NYou do your best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:53.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:588021,593360}I will. I don't think I've told you yet, but I was\Ntaken as an apprentice by Mr. Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.82,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:593360,595821}Yeah, I heard about it\Nfrom your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:595821,599074}But to be accurate, for now\NI'm mostly just a maid at his mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:601868,604704}On the upside, I make\N25.000 yen a month now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:604704,608542}I'm happy for you. It's great to have the chance\Nto study with a master of his caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:12.12,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:608542,612128}You don't have to worry about money\Nand can dedicate yourself to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:17.05,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:612128,617050}You can keep my scarf.\NIt's to celebrate and to bring you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:617050,618677}Huh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:20.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:618677,620762}Can I really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:620762,624057}Such beautiful colors.\NLike a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.60,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:624057,626601}A rainbow, huh…\NNow that I think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:626601,628603}Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.23,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:628603,630230}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:630230,632399}Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.73,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:632399,633733}You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:634776,636444}No. It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:636444,638989}I just thought about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:638989,642325}A rainbow is like\Na bridge over the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.20,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:642325,644202}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:49.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:644202,649749}I thought it would be nice if we had a beautiful\Nrainbow bridge that would connect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.59,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:652419,656590}I would never have imagined\Nthat you're such a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:00.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:656590,660552}What do you mean you would never\Nhave imagined? You're rude again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.38,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:660552,662387}Here you are, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.59,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:663013,664598}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.39,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:664598,666391}You've still got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.97,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:667601,668977}Yes sir.\NI'm going right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:668977,671021}You haven't finished\Nyour work yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.93,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:671021,672939}Yeah. I've gotta drive Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:672939,674941}Why do you have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.40,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:676109,677402}Sorry. Till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:30.41,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:685243,690415}{\fad(2000,0)}Mine Nozomi\NBehavior Research Report{NOTE:峰のぞみ\\N素行調査書}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.08,Default,Private investigator,0,0,0,,{TIME:691207,693084}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:37.96,Default,Private investigator,0,0,0,,{TIME:693084,697964}It's all the data on Mine Nozomi\NI've collected so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:697964,699215}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:699215,701217}Here's your payment for this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.39,Default,Private investigator,0,0,0,,{TIME:707390,708391}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.55,Default,Private investigator,0,0,0,,{TIME:708391,709559}See you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:12:00.77,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:715523,720779}{\i1}A budding couple full of hope\Nfor the future: Nozomi and Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:05.49,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:720779,725492}{\i1}That's the picture painted by the results of an\Ninvestigation by a detective Michiko has hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.41,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:725492,728411}{\i1}In an abnormal desire\Nfor misfortune and despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.91,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:728411,731915}{\i1}Michiko plans on how to tear up\Nthe relationship between Nozomi and Fanni.
Comment: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:13.66,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:733667,733667}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:734626,736419}Fanni Moriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:736419,738338}There's no one here by this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:738338,739839}Enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:739839,742258}I don't know about her\Nhooking up with any men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.96,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:742258,743969}But Mine is at the right age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:743969,745887}In any case, I completely trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.34,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:745887,747347}{\i1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.22,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:747347,749224}{\i1}Do you really trust her so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:32.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:749224,752060}I have better things to do\Nthan to listen to this trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.70,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:771121,773707}Hey, hey, look at him.\NHe's so handsome…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:776167,777502}Ah! Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.46,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:777502,779462}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:779462,780380}– Fanni.\N– Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:780380,782007}I'm surprised you found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.88,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:782007,784884}I was passing by\Nand I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:784884,786177}Thanks for dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:786177,790056}But is this okay?\NYou have an important match tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.76,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:790056,792767}I'll be fine.\NI'm gonna win, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:13.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:792767,793935}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:793935,797564}I'd like to talk with you,\Nbut I still have lots to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.85,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:797564,800859}I see. Let's meet some time\Nafter my match, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.90,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:800859,802902}Hey, hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.90,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:802902,806906}You should go with him.\NI'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:806906,808908}I don't know, I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.53,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:808908,811536}But he's came here\Njust for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:811536,813621}Alright then, just for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.70,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:813621,814706}Yeah. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:38.16,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:814706,818168}Master is away, too. Who knows\Nwhen you'll have the chance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:818168,820879}I'm sorry.\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:820879,822047}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.67,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:824340,825675}Just look at them…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.68,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:828970,830680}Say, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:830680,831973}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.85,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:831973,834851}It's been on my mind\Nsince the last time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:59.06,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:834851,839064}I was thinking how important\Nthis period is for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:839064,840565}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.10,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:840565,843109}We shouldn't rush anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:08.36,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:843109,848364}I was very happy that you came\Nto see me win the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:14.12,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:848364,854120}But it was only a very small victory\Ncompared to the whole career.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:857707,860919}I'm sorry, but could you\Nget off here and wait for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:860919,862545}I'm going to do a little work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:862545,863421}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.93,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:870929,872931}I'm here to deliver\Nthe car you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:46.11,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:883858,886111}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887904,889781}I mean, look at this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:889781,890907}It looks like a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.65,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:890907,892659}A prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.36,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:892659,894369}I like that. You nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.41,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:894369,896412}Haha. Spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.70,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:896412,899707}Hooray for our open blue sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:900500,902627}Fanni, wait for me.\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.17,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:902627,905171}Follow me, Nozomi!\NWe're escaping from prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:905171,906422}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:906422,907632}Wait for me, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:914389,918643}I feel like I understand\Nwhat you said before, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:24.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:920061,924149}What you tried to say is that rainbow\Nbridges are also very fleeting and fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:27.23,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:924149,927235}Yeah. The bridge between us\Nis very fragile as well. So…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:31.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:927235,931656}So we have to be careful\Nnot to risk destroying our balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.70,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:931656,933700}Yes. We have to be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:933700,935410}I agree, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:935410,938454}– But it's a pity.\N– I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:938454,941541}I'd love to meet with you\Nevery day, if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.58,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:941541,944586}But things just\Ndon't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:944586,945170}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.84,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:951342,953845}Ah, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:953845,954971}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.51,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:954971,957515}Nozomi-chan, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:00.31,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:957515,960310}Master just came back.\NHe knows you've sneaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:960310,961102}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:961102,962103}Mine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:962103,962896}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:962896,964355}Come here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:970904,972739}Can I know where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:16.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:972739,976409}The second I turn my back away, you forget\Nyour duties and go someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.20,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:976409,978203}What did I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.87,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:979037,981873}I told you to keep doing\Nthe vocal exercises when I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:981873,983166}Don't tell me you forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:984417,985793}But I did practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:985793,987795}I wouldn't come out\Nif I had anything left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:987795,989005}Spare me excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:990590,992800}You only do what you are told.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:992800,995220}You make a big mistake\Nif you think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:996930,997889}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:997889,999057}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:43.47,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:999057,1003478}You can't just do what I tell you.\NThe effort has to come from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:47.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003478,1007148}This is the most important thing\Nif you want to become a good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009692,1011110}Look inside this cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.48,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011110,1013488}It holds the souls of all those\Nwho preceded you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:56.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013488,1016491}They gave everything they had\Nfor the world of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016491,1018534}If you have the time\Nto play with your boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018534,1021329}why don't you listen\Nand study these records instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:04.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021329,1024165}But that's your treasured\Npersonal collection…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025166,1027126}It's not something to just look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:11.08,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027126,1031089}I'm always more than ready to share it\Nwith students who really want to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.09,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031089,1033091}But you look like\Nyou just want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034550,1036344}You have no right to judge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036344,1038846}Tomorrow Fanni\Nhas an important match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038846,1040265}We're serious in our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040265,1041557}You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041557,1044978}Is that how he prepares before a fight?\NBy hanging out with girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044978,1046396}What a worthless scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046396,1048481}Fanni is not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048481,1050066}Don't talk back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050066,1053820}If you really care about him that much,\Nthen how about you go sing just for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.98,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053820,1054988}You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054988,1057490}You should focus on music.\NOn music only!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:40.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057490,1060034}You have to forget\Neverything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060034,1061494}You don't understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061494,1062745}That's not how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062745,1064956}Fanni and me made a pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064956,1067000}Mine, you're not\Nlistening to me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.66,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067000,1068668}If you can't let go of that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068668,1070336}leave this mansion at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:50.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070336,1070628}Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.87,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070628,1071879}Please wait, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:54.00,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071879,1074007}I'm the one who let her sneak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074007,1075800}You stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.59,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075800,1077593}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.05,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077593,1079053}Ah, hurry up\Nand apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.63,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079053,1080638}I'll explain everything later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.09,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080638,1082098}Come on, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082098,1082849}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.26,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082849,1084267}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.81,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084267,1085810}Nozomi-cha…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085810,1087228}Let her do as she pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.89,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088396,1089897}Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.27,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089897,1091274}Come on, apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.27,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091274,1094277}If you do now,\NMaster can still forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094277,1095611}Sune-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095611,1097488}Sorry, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097488,1098364}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.32,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098364,1099324}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104370,1105913}{\i1}Why does it have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105913,1108291}{\i1}Even if it's Mr. Egawa,\NI won't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108291,1110251}{\i1}For Fanni's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.80,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118843,1121804}You don't want to go back?\NAre you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121804,1122722}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.76,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122722,1124766}Leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.47,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124766,1126476}I don't want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126476,1127143}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.39,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127143,1129395}I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129395,1130938}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130938,1132357}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132357,1133274}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133274,1135735}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135735,1136652}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136652,1138696}Open up…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.20,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142575,1144202}{\i1}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.37,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144202,1147372}{\i1}Come back when\Nyou become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.33,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147372,1149332}Why did you send her away, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.62,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149332,1151626}Will Sis return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.62,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151626,1153628}Ah, I guess she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.46,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154754,1156464}You didn't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.71,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156464,1159717}Sis has no other places to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.51,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162929,1164514}Where are you going, Kazuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.43,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164514,1166432}Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.43,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166432,1168434}Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.19,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1172772,1175191}– Sis!\N– Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.02,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175191,1177026}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.23,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177026,1179237}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.78,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185743,1186786}Ah, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.57,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186786,1188579}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.49,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1189163,1191499}– Sis! – Sis!\N– What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.00,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192333,1195002}You can't stay here, Sis.\NYou'll get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.04,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195002,1196045}You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.21,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196045,1197213}That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:00.04,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197213,1200049}We're worried about you.\NLet's get you somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:06.93,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203177,1206931}I see. So you'll go back\Nto Mr. Egawa's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207640,1209559}Huh? Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209559,1213479}But it's fine.\NYou don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.73,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213479,1215731}But I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.15,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215731,1217150}About Mom, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217150,1218860}What about Mom?\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.77,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218860,1220778}Her eyes have gotten a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220778,1222196}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:26.53,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222196,1226534}She can't even go out alone anymore.\NShe needs to get it treated soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226534,1229328}Why didn't you tell me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.37,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229328,1231372}Mom's said that we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:36.21,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231372,1236210}Because if we told you, you wouldn't\Nbe able to focus on your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236210,1237003}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240590,1242383}So that's how it is, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244510,1246846}Alright, I've got this.\NYou guys go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1246846,1247513}– Okay.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.68,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249098,1251684}Sis, don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.47,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251684,1253478}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.02,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253478,1255021}Yeah, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.14,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1256063,1257148}– Bye!\N– Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257148,1258316}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260735,1262820}Take care of Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.03,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1262820,1264030}– Yeah!\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.46,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278127,1280463}{\i1}Don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.04,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280463,1282048}{\i1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.05,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285092,1288054}{\i1}We shouldn't rush anything.\NIt's an important period for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291307,1294060}{\i1}Focus on music.\NOn music only!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305821,1307657}Hey, Sune! Where is my tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.65,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307657,1309659}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:54.91,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311827,1314914}Geez, I keep making you these\Nbut you never drink any.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314914,1316582}What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.37,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316582,1317375}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327385,1330263}What's with that tea?\NIt's boiling hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.34,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330263,1331347}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:15.14,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331347,1335142}It seems that you prefer tea\Nthe way Nozomi-chan prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.81,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335142,1336811}I-It has nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:22.73,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336811,1342733}I understand you more than you think.\NYou start to have regrets about your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342733,1344360}What regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347947,1349365}Sune, come here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:31.86,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350074,1351867}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.37,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355454,1356372}Master…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.79,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356372,1358791}Quickly, bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:39.87,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358791,1359875}C-Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:47.04,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365548,1367049}Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:48.63,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367049,1368634}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.17,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370928,1372179}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372179,1374140}Sune-chan, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374140,1376225}You'll tell me everything later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:57.72,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376225,1377727}Come on, step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:00.73,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377727,1380730}Look at you, all soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:01.81,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380730,1381814}Here.
